All error metrics are in Kelvin (K). Note: temperature differences in K equal differences in °C.

[metric_defs]
RMSE: sqrt(mean((pred - gt)^2)) over all pixels per sample
Max AE: max(abs(pred - gt)) over all pixels across the whole test set
RMSPE (%): 100 * sqrt(mean(((pred - gt)/gt)^2)) over pixels per sample, then averaged over batches
mean_grad: mean(|Sobel(pred) - Sobel(gt)|) (same as eval_guidance_ckpt.py)

